title: What Do The Celtics Need?
description:
Pablo Torre, Domonique Foxworth and David Jacoby debate if the Celtics are down 3-2 because Jayson Tatum hasn’t been good in the Finals and the chances the Bengals should be salty with Evan McPherson.
